Title: Visit the Las Vegas
subtitle: Of the future? By the future.
view-if: april_challenge = 1 and gambling_timer = 0 and difficulty < 1
tags: party_affairs
is-card: true
card-image: img/flags.jpg
new-page: true
on-arrival: month_actions += 1; gambling_timer = 12
go-to: room

@room

= Las Vegas

Visit me, Visit me. Give me your shares and values.

Theory stated that previously 99% of gamblers won in 99% of 0 of researched cases.

Thanks?

Anyways, use your resources. 

Currently you have: [+ resources +] resources.

